[
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c8",
    "created_time": "2025-10-09T05:04:49+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544774f",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Asha, the 06:40 traffic hit is running long lately. Let's tighten Lerato's cross to 90 seconds.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c7",
    "created_time": "2025-11-20T05:20:11+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185447750",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "resolved": "true",
    "text": "Agreed, Sipho. I'll signpost the sponsor read earlier so we don't crash the 09:00 handover.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c9",
    "created_time": "2025-11-07T06:54:27+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185447751",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "The outdoor vox pops have a lot of wind noise. I can clean them but the councillor's clip is unusable, can we re-record?",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c7",
    "created_time": "2025-10-02T07:12:03+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185447752",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Naledi, let's get the councillor on a clean phone line at 07:35 instead. Live is fine.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c8",
    "created_time": "2025-12-14T05:48:30+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185447753",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Wednesday looks light. Maybe move the throwback track to 07:45 so it lands in the school-run window?",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c9",
    "created_time": "2026-02-28T10:31:18+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185447754",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "resolved": "true",
    "text": "Mastered the Mandla trumpet segment. The 04:12 clip sounds gorgeous, exported a socials cut for you.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c7",
    "created_time": "2025-11-11T11:05:44+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185447755",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "resolved": "true",
    "text": "Perfect, thank you Naledi. Palesa will want this for the station socials.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463ca",
    "created_time": "2025-12-07T08:22:09+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185447756",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Rev. Moyo's street kitchens piece is getting great listener response. Can we line up the follow-up for July?",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c7",
    "created_time": "2025-10-01T09:40:55+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185447757",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f8",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Love the love-letters-to-Joburg idea. Pitching it to Dr. Khumalo at Monday's planning meeting.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c8",
    "created_time": "2026-02-05T06:15:27+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185447758",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Taxi rank soundscapes could be a killer Off-Mic special. Kagiso has a great shotgun mic for the field work.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463cc",
    "created_time": "2026-01-27T07:02:14+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185447759",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f9",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Happy to bring the rig. Bree Street rank is busiest around 06:00, good ambient texture early.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463ca",
    "created_time": "2025-11-11T13:18:41+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544775a",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fa",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Reached out to Nandi's agent. She's keen on a July Tuesday VOTC slot, waiting on dates.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463d1",
    "created_time": "2025-11-08T15:30:09+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544775b",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fb",
    "resolved": "true",
    "text": "Confirmed for the in-studio chat. Kgosi Media is fully behind the Off-Mic launch, let's talk branding.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c7",
    "created_time": "2026-03-27T08:11:52+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544775c",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fc",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "First pass at the hero headline is too stiff. Going to rewrite it in my own voice tonight.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c9",
    "created_time": "2026-01-08T16:55:33+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544775d",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464fd",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Studio B is free Thursday afternoon for the pilot masters. I'll target -16 LUFS for the podcast platforms.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c8",
    "created_time": "2026-03-28T12:44:20+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544775e",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185446500",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Found the 1996 launch tape in the Kgosi Media archive for the 30th doc. Quality is rough but usable for the November shoot.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463cb",
    "created_time": "2026-03-04T18:02:47+02:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544775f",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185446502",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Library winter drive sponsor read is approved. Good cause, glad we're running it all week, Asha.",
    "parent_block_id": "root"
  },
